title: 30 Minute Calorie Burning Elliptical Elixir Workout
description:
Make some time for yourself today and hop on your elliptical! This 30-minute elliptical elixir with Sunny Trainer Brittany Noelle is the perfect way to mix up your routine and get some great low-impact cardio in. Sunny fam, let’s get this!

Sunny Trainer: Brittany Noelle
